<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA44">
<l>taṉakkē yaṭiyaṉāyt taṉṉaṭaintu vāḻu</l>
<l>meṉakkē yaruḷāvā ṟeṉkoṉ - maṉakkiṉiya</l>
<l>cīrāḷaṉ kaṅkai maṇavāḷaṉ cemmēṉip</l>
<l>pērāḷaṉ vāṉōr pirāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What is [this] way of not being gracious towards me</l>
<l>who lives approaching him as his servant – in the lord</l>
<l>of the celestials, the great man with red body, the husband</l>
<l>of the Gaṅgā, the excellent man pleasing to the mind?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
